Learn how to make your own padded headboard with a few simple steps. In this video tutorial, interior designer Joanna Lavén shows you the complete process of building your elegant headboard, from choosing the velvet curtain covering the panels to how you mount the headboard to the wall. Happy DIY!

To watch this tutorial in its original version with subtitles, head over to the H&M HOME Youtube channel — link in bio! #HMHOME #bedroominterior #bedroominspo #headboard

node.title: DIY: How to make an elegant headboard 🤍💫
